## Dashboard 1 — Market Overview & Investment Intelligence

**4 KPI Tiles:** Total Listings · Median Nightly Price · Market Avg Occupancy % · Market Avg RevPAR

**4 Charts:**
- 🗺️ **Choropleth Map** — Revenue by neighbourhood (colour intensity = avg revenue)
- 🌳 **Treemap** — Market share by Room Type, coloured by avg revenue (shows *gap* between supply share and revenue share)
- 📊 **Horizontal Bar** — Top 15 neighbourhoods by `investment_potential` score (your most actionable chart for investors)
- 📦 **Stacked Bar** — Listing count by Price Tier × Room Type (shows market gaps)

---

## Dashboard 2 — Revenue & Pricing Strategy

**5 KPI Tiles:** Avg Revenue · Median Occupancy % · Avg RevPAR · 90th Percentile Revenue · Superhost Revenue Premium %

**5 Charts:**
- 🔵 **Scatter Plot** — Price vs Revenue (coloured by room type, sized by occupancy) → finds the **sweet spot price**
- 📦 **Box & Whisker** — Revenue distribution per Price Tier → reveals if "charge more = earn more" is actually true
- 📊 **Bar + Reference Line** — RevPAR by neighbourhood vs market median (professional hotel industry metric)
- 📊📈 **Dual-Axis Combo** — Revenue (bar) + Occupancy % (line) by room type → high revenue + low occupancy = underpriced
- 🔥 **Highlight Table** — Revenue Tier × Neighbourhood (which areas concentrate top earners)

---

## Dashboard 3 — Host Performance & Guest Experience

**5 KPI Tiles:** Avg Overall Rating · % Superhosts · Avg Reviews/Month · Instant Bookable % · Avg Acceptance Rate

