- 📊 **Rating Histogram** — Distribution across rating categories (where is the market clustered?)
- 📊 **Side-by-Side Bar** — Superhost vs Non-Superhost across 4 metrics (quantifies the Superhost badge value)
- 🎯 **Bullet Charts** — Sub-scores vs market avg (Accuracy, Cleanliness, Check-in, Communication, Location, Value)
- 🔵 **Strategic Scatter** — Reviews/Month (X) vs Rating (Y), 4 quadrants: Stars / Hidden Gems / Volume Players / Underperformers ← **most powerful chart**
- 📊 **Bar** — Top 15 neighbourhoods by avg rating, coloured by % Superhost density
- 📊 **Grouped Bar** — Instant Bookable YES vs NO → impact on Revenue, Rating, Occupancy

